
COMMAND:
   death <victim> or just death during the fight.

ART:
  death is the strongest attack of the monk against a single
  victim. This means for many very weak victims instant death.
  For stronger victims it means you do awful damage, but you
  will 'hurt yourself too' using this attack. The death won't
  work that bad on players.

COST:
   variable

POWER:
   dexterity/skill depending
